mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SQUARE DANCES "Exactly Like You", "Don't Blame It All on Me", "Birds of a Feather", and "Past One" ROUND DANCES "Submarine Waltz" and "Wallaby Walk" SPECIAL FEATURES "A Chance to 'Seii' Square Dancing", "The Silver Spur Award", "The Fashion Future of Square Dancing", "Some Callers in Canada", "The Double Square", "Your Week at Asilomar", "Press-Time Bulletins from San Diego", "Hula to Hoe-Down", and "Co-operation Does It!" This edition also includes the the regular features entitled "As I see it", "The Square Dance Picture", "The Square of the Month", "Round the Outside Ring", "From the Floor" and "Calendar of Square Dancing Events".
